Subject: [PATCH] board: ti: am64x: assign MCU GPIO router to MAIN_0_R5_1

This patch captures a workspace change from
`workspace/ti-u-boot-sdk12`.

Intent:
- preserve the Phase2 U-Boot change as a selectable asset in the Main Repo
- avoid treating the mutable workspace tree as the long-term source of truth

This change is explicitly adopted into the U-Boot replay set through
`bsp/u-boot/patches/series`, while still remaining a selectable BSP asset
rather than an automatic final-product baseline.
